subtitleNullable: Predict the future blood glucose values
descriptionNullable:
This data was collected as part of a study on BG prediction and BG dynamics analysis. It contains blood glucose values, insulin dosage, carbohydrate intake, and physiological data of a single patient with type 1 diabetes. In total it covers approximately 5 months and was collected in free-living conditions.

Data may be used to train ML models for BG prediction, that is, time series forecasting.
